title: EpicBot 520 Mirror (March 17 2012)
description:
Epicbot version 520

This is a mirror for the current website, as it is currently undergoing a distributed denial of service. This event causes the servers to be overloaded so users cannot access the website.

Treat this download like a mirror to the real download on the website.

Have fun botting. If you have any questions, ask on the forums when they come back up.

JRE 7 Required.
